        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Tribal Energy Investment Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Energy to provide direct loans to Indian tribes and tribal energy development organizations for energy development. These direct loans shall be made through the Federal Financing Bank.</p>]]>
        </text>
